name: Malik Sabor ROSS, Petitioner v. Hon. Arnold L. NEW, Judge, Respondent

parties: Malik Sabor ROSS, Petitioner v. Hon. Arnold L. NEW, Judge, Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 13th day of November, 2014, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is DIRECTED to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
